    • getQuery

      public java.lang.String getQuery​(java.lang.annotation.Annotation[] annotations)
      Takes an array of annotations and searches for a GraphQuery instance. If an instance is found it will then look for an entry that matches GraphQuery.value() and if not found will return null.
      Parameters:
      annotations - an array of annotations that should contain GraphQuery.
      Returns:
      the contents of a template file or null if no entry is found.
